Episodes
The War Doctor faces the Daleks in four seasons of the Time War.
The War Doctor
Series 1: Only the Monstrous (2015)
| ShortSummary    = The Doctor is discovered injured on the planet Keska and is nursed back to health by Rejoice. The planet comes under attack from an enemy and the Doctor assists with the defence.
