| ShortSummary    = The Doctor investigates strange events in the Obsidian Nebula, which reveals that his old companion Leela is still alive despite being presumed dead in the early days of the Time War.
| LineColor       = 321C16
}}
| ShortSummary    = The Doctor, Leela and Ollistra must protect Gallifrey from an other-dimensional assault organised by the Daleks.
| LineColor       = 321C16
